    "description": "We at Torrent Pharmaceuticals Consulting Pvt Ltd are looking for an experienced Consultant Physician based out of Surat. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Torrent Pharmaceuticals Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nTorrent Pharmaceuticals Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Torrent Pharmaceuticals Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
